metadata.name: RYUSEI
metadata.description:
Even though this is only my imagination, not a single thing is real.

Just having you with me is more than enough.

Let a cold breeze blow on us as you watch me paint this world with my life, just like a shooting star burning through the sky.

Even if it is only one blink in a vast expanse of time, even if it feels like a dream that will surely fade away someday, please.

Our feeling is real, no matter what.

So, only this night, please take my hand.

"Together with me, to an ending we aim for."

Size : 2123 x 2473
